title: Nat Speeches V.1
author: WojtekPaint
pages:
#- 

Speech Transcripts
from the Nationalist
Internationale at
Volkstadt, Volume 1
#- Volkstadt Square. 6th Sept, 2015, 6:01 EST.§0
§0
§0Kovio and ImmerRichtig stand on the balcony overlooking the crowds in the square below. I stand with Aufdenstadt and bgbba on the side of the balcony. Kovio announces the start of the Internationale:
#- Kovio: We're starting.§0
§0
§0ImmerRichtig: Hello and welcome. For those of you who don't know me, I am ImmerRichtig – leader and third fuhrer of Polynesia. I'd like to give a warm welcome to all attending.§0
§0
§0Those of you in attendance subscribe
#- to the third position - monarchy, fascism, national socialism, and various associated ideologies.§0
§0
§0Authoritarian ideologies lend a certain amount of trust to a figurehead. This is a two way street. Citizens must have faith that their leaders make the best
#- decisions for their nation. And leaders must protect and give the tools needed to empower their citizens so they can achieve their hopes, dreams and desires in life.§0
§0
§0* At this point, the would-be assassin Deletethis, who has scaled the Volkstadt town
#- hall and stands above us on the balcony, fires an arrow down and knocks Immer from the balcony. *§0
§0
§0OutcastMephisto: OH NO§0
§0
§0ImmerRichtig: Wow. JFK right now.§0
§0
§0* About a minute's worth of commotion as Immer returns to the
#- balcony. *§0
§0
§0ImmerRichtig (fearlessly shaking of his wounds, like a fascist Teddy Roosevelt): Shall I continue?§0 *Numerous cries of "aye!"* Okay. :DD§0
§0
§0I am a firm believer - family notwithstanding - there is no greater
#- pride than pride in one's nation - no greater love than love of one's volk, one's people. In civcraft we have the opportunity to create our own societies, craft our own nations and empires and play a direct role in how they are run. The crowd in
#- attendance today proves this is more than just a fringe point of view. Going forward, know that you are not alone in your views, know that there is nothing wrong with loving your your nation - §0
§0
§0Kovio: Or loving your people~
#- ImmerRichtig: - and know that there is nothing wrong with taking pride in your people.§0
§0
§0I wish you all a prosperous future - in civcraft and beyond. Enjoy Viridian Day everyone!§0
§0
§0* Crowd cheers. *
#- ImmerRichtig: If Kovio doesn't have anything to say, then Cast will talk about how he came to appreciate nationalism from his communist origins.§0
§0
§0Kovio: I have no words~. Just happiness.§0
§0
§0Quahtli Mia: I'ma make up a speech.
#- Improvisation.§0
§0
§0ImmerRichtig: Cast isn't ready, so everyone take a bathroom break now.§0
§0
§0* Bathroom break. At this point, ApacheClitz begins his killing spree. Numerous spectators are killed, and the square erupts into panic. Apache flees,
#- heading down the road from Volkstadt towards Xiphias. VitaCoco and MC pursue him along with several Polynesians, and the terrorist is soon pearled. *§0
§0
§0Kovio: THE TERRORIST HAS BEEN CAPTURED§0
§0

#- OutcastMephisto: THROUGH OUR INTERNATIONAL SOLIDARITY§0
§0
§0* Celebration ensues. A group picture is taken on the stairs of the town hall, with MC and Vita proudly displaying the pearl of the terrorist, who has been identified as a Wheat Crew member. *
#- WojtekPaint: Speech!§0
§0Speech!§0
§0Speech!§0
§0
§0Kovio: Blue, speech.§0
§0
§0Bgbba: Speech from Blue!§0
§0
§0* BlueSylvaer, dictator of Hjaltland, ascends to the balcony *§0
§0
§0BlueSylvaer: Okay.
#- Bgbba: Everybody quiet. Blue's got a speech.§0
§0
§0BlueSylvaer: When most people think of Nationalism, they immediately think we're dumb or crazy, because no one on earth can possibly have the tenacity to have respect for a single national
#- identity. They're wrong. Nationalism brings us all closer, Eden and Nox, Chanada and Hjaltland, people who had no business with each other in the first place.§0
§0
§0* Applause *§0
§0
§0We need to secure our ideology. We need to show pride for our
#- nations, not only by ourselves, but in solidarity with our fellow fascists.§0
§0
§0* Deletethis returns at this point and causes a minor disturbance. Blue continues on unfazed. *§0
§0
§0BlueSylvaer: When you have the faith to give one man a massive
#- amount of power, that is the biggest step of identity any nation can take. We create a national pride. National pride is ideal or else we all look like cowards. We look like crazy fools who run around saying Sieg Heil.
#- MegraLew (communist visitor): That's because you are.§0
§0
§0BlueSylvaer: There's more to nationalism and authoritarianism than what others think. And it is by far the most respectable and alpha ideology on the server. Glory to Polynesia! Glory to Hjaltland!
#- BlueSylvaer: Thank you.§0
§0
§0* Enthusiastic applause. *§0
§0
§0Camokool: Heil Nationalist Internationale!§0
§0
§0Kovio: HAPPY VIRIDIAN DAY! GOD BLESS CHANADA!§0

#- BlueSylvaer: HAPPY VIRIDIAN DAY!§0
§0
§0Phlower: MY LIFE FOR BLUESYLAVER§0
§0
§0Bgbba: *cries patriotically*§0
§0
§0* Qua ascends to the balcony. *§0
§0
§0Quauhtli Mia: Is anyone else having speech
#- but me now? Jesus I'm so nervous.§0
§0
§0BlueSylvaer: You'll do fine.§0
§0
§0* People in the square causing a minor commotion. *§0
§0
§0Qua: Tell me when I'm doing my speech. I'll wait if I need to.§0

#- Bgbba: Qua is giving a speech! Everyone shut it!§0
§0
§0WojtekPaint: Speech!§0
§0Speech! Speech!§0
§0
§0ImmerRichtig: Qua, go ahead when you are ready.§0
§0
§0* Camo pearls deletethis, the source of the commotion. *
#- Qua: Ooohh kaay, I'm going to be honest guys, I'm nervous as shit... but here it goes.§0
§0
§0ImmerRichtig: You've got this Qua.§0
§0
§0Qua: Hello guys. I'm Quauhtli, Third Chieftain and first Alcuahtl of Yoahtl. For several years, Yoahtl has survived by hopping
#- across server to server. Should be nine now. Before me it was Wichita, and before him was Eoahtl. We all kept going, believing in the idea of Yoahtl. We lost friends and many people trying to keep this idea alive. In wars, conflicts. And sometimes actual
#- friends.§0
§0
§0In E.C we had a server wide war KEEPING our way alive only to have the server die later. But despite this we moved to another, Melonia or Meloncraft. Because we believed in our ways. We believed that if we had hope, and faith in our
#- identity: as a people. Not as a clan, not as a gamer group. But as a real and ACTIVE community of people willing to help and defend each other despite any diffence or deviation. This way has gone for nine years, before me and hopefully after.
#- I am here because -§0
§0because I see that fire in everyone here.§0
§0
§0*Applause.*§0
§0
§0We came to Civian after melonia started to die because you people have this tenacity.§0
§0
§0* Enthusiastic applause. *
#- You people have this fire, this will to keep going depspite any kind of obstacle. And from this I know that what keeps our ways alive, especially as a community, is the willingless and tenacity to keep going despite ANY KIND OF DISRUPTION OR OBSTACLE.
#- And with this I am proud to call Civian, Civcraft, Yoahtl's new home.

* Enthusiastic applause. MegraLew, the visiting communist, sets up a table of cakes as a gift. *

Qua: Kovio, do you think I did good? ;-;
#- Immer: Yes. It was a good speech Qua.

Kovio: You did good Qua.
#- [This volume is the first transcribing the speeches given at the Nationalist International, hosted at Volkstadt on the 6th of September 2015, in celebration of the first anniversary of the founding of Viridian. The preceding text documents the first three
#- speeches given at the meeting, all through in-game text. Two other speeches - a longer biographical about by Cast424 and short closing statement by Kovio - followed those given here, and will be available in a future volume. The transcriber of this
#- volume has compiled the speeches and accounts of that day from his chat logs and his own memory of the event; some liberties were taken in the transcription with respect to grammar, capitalization and punctuation, but the original words were adhered to as
#- closely as possible. The picture taken at the steps of the Volkstadt town hall is available on the /r/Civcraft subreddit. If you are interested further in the ideas touched upon in the speeches presented above, look out for any works published by the
#- speechwriters or by other Polynesians.

This document was transcribed by WojtekPaint. Long live Chanada.]
#- 